explanation: A table listing adjusted vaccine effectiveness (VE) estimates for RIV4 compared to no vaccination, for standard-dose inactivated influenza vaccine quadrivalent (SD-IIV4) compared to no vaccination, and the relative VE of RIV4 versus SD-IIV4 overall and by subgroup (sex, age, risk condition, season).
